134 493 :M
f4_12 sf
(, so-called )S
f1_12 sf
(subsets)S
f4_12 sf
( are used to choose reactions. Subsets are)S
89 506 :M
(temporary lists of reactions used for searching etc. After that, some or all)S
89 519 :M
(reactions from a subset can be 'copied' into the main window. Besides)S
89 532 :M
